no.bekk.bekkopen.person
Class Fodselsnummer

java.lang.Object
  no.bekk.bekkopen.common.StringNumber
      no.bekk.bekkopen.person.Fodselsnummer

public class Fodselsnummer
extends StringNumber

This class represent a Norwegian social security number - a Fodselsnummer. A Fodselsnummer consists of 11 digits, where the first 6 digits contains the date of birth and the last 5 consists of an Individnummer (3 digits) and two checksum digits.

Author:
Per K. Mengshoel
